<h2 id=3D"id-03SD:BeneficiaryPhase2:Upliftpaymentinitiation-KeyDecisions"><=
span>Key Decisions</span></h2>
<p><br></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"relative-table wrapped confluenceTable" style=3D"width: 96.=
5327%;">
<colgroup class=3D"">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 3.08037%;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 32.2888%;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 44.7224%;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 12.2644%;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 7.64389%;">
</colgroup>
<thead class=3D"">
<tr class=3D"">
<th style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTh">=
<p>Ref #</p></th>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTh">=
<p>Decision</p></th>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTh">=
<p>Description</p></th>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTh">=
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">Decision made by</span></p></th>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTh">=
<p>Date</p></th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody class=3D"">
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
#001</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<span data-teams=3D"true">Decision on the direction of the PayID counting s=
ervice as temporary solution (before SAFI takes over the limit decision)<br=
></span></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<ol>
<li><strong>INF API</strong>: Uses a database table as a "counting service"=
.</li>
<li><strong>EXP API (August)</strong>:=20
<ol>
<li>Calls the counting service to get the next count.</li>
<li>Checks if the count is less than 50; if not, throws an error.</li>
<li>If the count is valid, calls the downstream payment API.</li>
</ol></li>
<li><strong>Future Considerations</strong>:=20
<ul>
<li>Suggests not creating a "limit validation service" since SAFI expects t=
o be told the count and then decides if the request is allowed or denied.</=
li>
<li>In November, step 2b might be replaced by a call to SAFI.</li>
<li>Alternatives include:=20
<ul>
<li>Ping Authorise calling the counting service and then SAFI, but this may=
 impact performance.</li>
<li>UI sending the count to Ping Authorise, but this could fail security te=
sts due to potential manipulation.</li>
</ul></li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
<p><br></p>
<p>Updates:</p>
<p>&nbsp;<time datetime=3D"2025-05-13" class=3D"date-past">13 May 2025</tim=
e> - Architecture decision has been made for EXP API to call SAFI.</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>Counts are still maintained and retrieved from COSMICS.</li>
<li>Any counter reset is still being done in the counting service.&nbsp;</l=
i>
<li>SAFI maintains the limit and enforces the decision for the limit.&nbsp;=
</li>
<li>EXP API triggers SAFI for the decision whether the calls to the downstr=
eam is allowed.&nbsp;</li>
</ul>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><a class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"M064489" =
href=3D"/display/~M064489" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1920714325" data-link=
ed-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-=
url=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Edmond Tso</a> <a class=3D"co=
nfluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"M058573" href=3D"/display/=
~M058573" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1125291984" data-linked-resource-versi=
on=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-url=3D"https://co=
nfluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Ave Cahyadi</a>&nbsp;</p>
<p><span data-teams=3D"true"><a class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" =
data-username=3D"M062050" href=3D"/display/~M062050" data-linked-resource-i=
d=3D"1515690289" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-ty=
pe=3D"userinfo" data-base-url=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">And=
rew Suduk</a>&nbsp;</span></p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><time datetime=3D"2025-04-23" class=3D"date-past">23 Apr 2025</time>&nbs=
p;</p>
</div></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
