<h1 id=3D"id-03SD:BeneficiaryPhase2:Upliftpaymentinitiation-Solution"><span=
>Solution</span></h1>
<h2 id=3D"id-03SD:BeneficiaryPhase2:Upliftpaymentinitiation-SolutionOvervie=
w"><span>Solution Overview</span></h2>
<p><span>The Solution covers at the following scenarios:</span></p>
<ol>
<li>Payment MFE:=20
<ol>
<li>The payment MFE that needs to be uplifted to integrate with the Benefic=
iary Management INF API. ( to create new EXP API to get data from the Benef=
iciary INF API (<a href=3D"https://mesh.westpac.com.au/components/apis/bene=
ficiary-management-v1" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">beneficiary=
-management-v1</a>) )</li>
</ol></li>
<li>Payment EXP API:=20
<ol>
<li>uplift of the payment API to fetch data from the Beneficiary data store=
 instead of the legacy beneficiary solution.&nbsp;(<a href=3D"https://mesh.=
westpac.com.au/components/datastores/inf-bnkng-arrngmnt-chnlaccsarrngmnt-in=
stl-payee-v1?tab=3Ddependency&amp;previousComponentName=3Dinf-bnkng-arrngmn=
t-chnlaccsarrngmnt-instl-payee-v1" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow"=
